        {
            "+content": "In the 1910s, Kodō Iwamoto is a third-year student at Seihō Middle School, which is directly controlled by the military and dedicated to collecting and researching supernatural phenomena to harness that power for military use. Under military orders, Kodō travels across the country to investigate supernatural phenomena. In one town where it is rumored that \"black snow\" falls, he meets a boy who thinks his mysterious powers are an illness. Kodō shows the boy how to use his powers and offers him a letter of recommendation to Seihō Middle School. As he travels to other areas, Kodō encounters many other mysterious events.",
